<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Apollo 14 Astronaut Presents UCF Student with Scholarship</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By UCF Staff
		
		<span class="date">Updated Nov. 19, 2007</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 196px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1236/en_US/bencrop.jpg" height="261" width="196"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Courtesy of Benjamin Corbin</p>
			
			<p>Benjamin Corbin is the 16th UCF student to win a scholarship from the Astronaut Scholarship Foundation.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041045494c8d01161d3164c1007d28">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
								<h3>Story Images</h3>
								<ul id="story_images">
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041045494c8d01161d3164c1007d28&amp;img_mode=1&amp;index=0">
							<img width="100" alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1236/en_US/mitchellfull.jpg"  />
						</a>
						</li>
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			</ul><p  class="note">Click thumbnails for full-size images.</p>
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
			<div id="related">
				<h3>Related Contacts and Links:</h3>
