			</ul>
		
		</li>
	
	
	
		
		<li>
		
			<h4><a href="http://www.honors.ucf.edu">UCF's Burnett Honors College</a></h4>
		
		</li>
	
		
		<li>
		
			<h4><a href="http://www.AstronautScholarship.org">Astronaut Scholarship Foundation</a></h4>
		
		</li>
	
	
